{"lemma":"عَلاةُ","slug":"عَلاةُ","root":"ع.ل.#","root_slug":"ع-ل-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ل-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n30392","n30409"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"singulative of عَلًا (ʕalan)","tags":["form-of","singulative"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"large she-camel"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n30392","headword_ar":"علّاهُ","root":"Elw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 4. ―         -b2-  [Hence,] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eal~ayotu","text_ar":"عَلَّيْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi EalaY AlbaEiyri","text_ar":"بِهِ عَلَى البَعِيرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I raised it, and put it, upon the camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) [and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAlayotuhu","text_ar":"عَالَيْتُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as in a verse cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAy^iHN","text_ar":"رَايِحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rwH","text_ar":"روح"},{"kind":"text","text":"; in which, and in the present art., it is cited in the S and TA: and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAlabotu","text_ar":"عَالَبْتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi","text_ar":"بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as in a verse cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY","text_ar":"اـِلَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino","text_ar":"مِنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alw","text_ar":"الو"},{"kind":"text","text":":] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY~a","text_ar":"عَلَىَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAli","text_ar":"عَالِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiHomilo","text_ar":"اِحْمِلْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Put thou upon me"},{"kind":"text","text":"such a thing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to be carried by me;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"load thou me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, K.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eal~ayotu","text_ar":"عَلَّيْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHabola","text_ar":"الحَبْلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEoliyapN","text_ar":"تَعْلِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I raised the cord to its proper place in respect of the channel of the sheave, and in respect of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"main"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"well-rope."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"El~Y Ald~alowa","text_ar":"علّى الدَّلْوَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He raised the bucket from a stone projecting in the lower part of the casing of a well"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and impeding its ascent"},{"kind":"text","text":"];"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he having descended the well for that purpose:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or simply"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he raised the filled bucket;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for] some say that ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmuEal~iY","text_ar":"المُعَلِّى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he who raises the filled bucket;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who draws water thereby."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"El~Y AlmataAEa Eani Ald~aAb~api","text_ar":"علّى المَتَاعَ عَنِ الدَّابَّةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put down the goods,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"furniture and utensils, from the beast:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. because he who does so lifts them off the beast:] (K, TA:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEolaAhu","text_ar":"اَعْلَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this sense is disapproved. (TA.) ―         -b6-  See also 1, former half. ―         -b7-  And see Q. Q. 1."}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n30409","headword_ar":"عَلَاةٌ","root":"Elw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sinodaAn","text_ar":"سِنْدَان"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anvil"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S, Mgh, K, TA,) whether"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$jr","text_ar":"شجر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as are made from trees,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or perhaps this is a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Saxor","text_ar":"صَخْر"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rock"},{"kind":"text","text":"], or of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"iron;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuborap","text_ar":"زُبْرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"iron anvil"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon which the blacksmith beats iron:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl. [or rather coll. gen. n.] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalFA","text_ar":"عَلًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) ―         -b2-  Hence it is applied to a she-camel, as being likened thereto in respect of her hardness: you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAqapN EalaApu Alxaloqi","text_ar":"نَاقَةٌ عَلَاةُ الخَلْقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A she-camel hard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"firm, in respect of make"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaApN","text_ar":"عَلَاةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus applied signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tall,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overtopping;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiloyaAnN","text_ar":"عِلْيَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eil~iyaAnN","text_ar":"عِلِّيَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, TA:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiloyaAnN","text_ar":"عِلْيَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaloyaAnN","text_ar":"عَلْيَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eil~iyaAnN","text_ar":"عِلِّيَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) signify, thus applied,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tall and bulky;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA;) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"outstripping in pace"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"journeying; never seen otherwise than before the other camels."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A stone"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"placed upon two other stones called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HimaAraAni","text_ar":"حِمَارَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(q. v.)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon which is put"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to dry the preparation of curd called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqiT","text_ar":"اَقِط"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K, TA:) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece of rock upon which is made a circle of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axovaA='","text_ar":"اَخْثَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lumps of dung such as is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xivoY","text_ar":"خِثْى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(q. v.)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and bricks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crude bricks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"labin","text_ar":"لَبِن"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and ashes, and in,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon, which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqaT","text_ar":"اَقَط"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is then cooked:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. [or coll. gen. n.] as above. (TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing like the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"milking-vessel called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eulobap","text_ar":"عُلْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"around which"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dung such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xivoY","text_ar":"خِثْى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is put, and which is used for milking therein."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}